HEADWORD: Biotite
<hw>Bi"o*tite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Biot</ets>, a French naturalist.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Mica
